       <h2>Who is developing Salsa?</h2>

      <p>Salsa is an open source web application being developed at <a href="http://usu.edu/">Utah State University</a>. The Salsa project team is located at the <a href="http://cidi.usu.edu/">Center for Innovative Design &amp; Instruction</a>. The Salsa project has received funding from the <a href="http://ustar.usu.edu/">Utah Science and Technology Research</a> initiative.<p>
      <p>Contact the project at <a href="mailto:salsa@usu.edu">salsa@usu.edu.</a>
